upstream tarball was generated from the git repo using:

* retrieving most recent sha1 from gitweb, since the dumb http server
  used does not systematically update refs for "git fetch"
* fetch it:
	git fetch origin $sha:refs/remotes/origin/hidden
* lay tags for interesting versions:
	git tag 0.17 origin/hidden -m 0.17
* create tarball:
	(V=origin/hidden; git archive --prefix=hachu-$(git describe $V)/ \
            --format=tar.gz -o ../hachu_$(git describe $V).orig.tar.gz $V)
